OL,3,CVictims to attend parole hearings in
OL,4,CUK-wide rollout of 'vital' scheme
OL,6,FVictims will now be able to attend
OL,7,Fparole hearings of criminals following
OL,8,Fa successful pilot scheme in Greater
OL,9,FManchester.
OL,11,FThe national rollout, which comes into
OL,12,Fforce across England and Wales on
OL,13,FTuesday 1 April, is designed to boost
OL,14,Fconfidence in the justice system.
OL,16,FThe reform will allow victims to apply
OL,17,Fto attend private hearings held to
OL,18,Fdecide whether a prisoner can be
OL,19,Freleased from jail.
