OL,3,CVictims to attend parole hearings in
OL,4,CUK-wide rollout of 'vital' scheme
OL,6,FThe pilot scheme which took place in
OL,7,FGreater Manchester and South West of
OL,8,FEngland, found that victims were
OL,9,F"reassured" to see the process of
OL,10,Foffenders being held to account before
OL,11,Fthe Parole Board made a decision
OL,12,Fwhether to release them under licence
OL,13,Fconditions.
OL,15,FA victim known as Anna, who attended a
OL,16,Fparole hearing during the pilot
OL,17,Finitiative, said witnessing the care
OL,18,Ftaken by the panel gave her "genuine
OL,19,Fconfidence" in how the perpetrator
OL,20,Fwould be managed once released from
OL,21,Fcustody.
