OL,3,CVictims to attend parole hearings in
OL,4,CUK-wide rollout of 'vital' scheme
OL,6,FShe said: "It helped us draw a line
OL,7,Funder the whole chapter and move on".
OL,9,FVictims will not be able to observe
OL,10,Fthe entire hearing as certain evidence
OL,11,Fsuch as on risk management must be
OL,12,Fheard in private.
OL,14,FThe process also hears evidence on the
OL,15,Foffender's behaviour in prison and
OL,16,Fwork they are doing to stop committing
OL,17,Ffurther crimes.
