OL,3,CVictims to attend parole hearings in
OL,4,CUK-wide rollout of 'vital' scheme
OL,6,FVictims' commissioner Baroness Newlove
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a vital step towards
OL,8,Flifting the lid on a system that has
OL,9,Flong felt closed off to victims,
OL,10,Fhelping them feel more meaningfully
OL,11,Finvolved rather than bystanders to
OL,12,Fproceedings."
OL,14,FNew measures are expected to be
OL,15,Fintroduced later this year for
OL,16,Fministers to be given more power over
OL,17,Fthe release of the most serious
OL,18,Fcriminals, by being able to refer
OL,19,Fcertain cases to the High Court for a
OL,20,Fsecond check.
