OL,3,CVictims to attend parole hearings in
OL,4,CUK-wide rollout of 'vital' scheme
OL,6,FVictims minister Alex Davies-Jones
OL,7,Fsaid: "For too long, victims have been
OL,8,Flocked out of the parole system.
OL,10,F"As part of our plan for change, we
OL,11,Fare now giving victims the right to
OL,12,Fsee how offenders are challenged when
OL,13,Fup for parole.
OL,15,F"This Government is improving our
OL,16,Fjustice system to ensure it serves
OL,17,Fvictims better."
