OL,3,CVictims to attend parole hearings in
OL,4,CUK-wide rollout of 'vital' scheme
OL,6,FThe Parole Board is an independent
OL,7,Fbody that assesses whether prisoners
OL,8,Fcan be safely released from jail into
OL,9,Fthe community, and on what licence
OL,10,Fconditions such as curfews, as well as
OL,11,Frecommending whether inmates can be
OL,12,Fmoved to an open prison.
OL,14,FChief executive officer Cecilia French
OL,15,Fsaid: "I understand just how important
OL,16,Faccess to information is to victims
OL,17,Fand survivors.
